cs.SY, cs.CE, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.LG

The paper introduces a new language for programming deterministic chemical kinetics to perform computation, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) as well as computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE). The paper also discusses the syntax and semantics of the language, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper presents methods to minimize error and implement error analysis tools, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) as well as machine learning (cs.LG).
